Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.90,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Lựa chọn duy nhất là ra ngoài và leo xuống.{Our only options are to start descending the cliff face,}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.32,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Có cái hang nào gần không...?{Any other holes nearby...?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.16,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Cái đó thì sao?{How about that one?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.58,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nơi mà lũ sinh vật nhỏ thải phân!{The spot with the critter droppings sticking out!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.54,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Riko, được rồi!{Riko, go ahead now!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.58,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Ừ!{Alright!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.38,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi nhé...{Sorry...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.96,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Giá mà được chế biến bọn mi thành món gì ngon ngon.{I would have rather made a delicious meal}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.89,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Không bay được trên trời, không chạy được trên tường,{Unable to fly in the sky or run on walls,}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:35.23,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,chúng ta đơn giản chỉ là được chọn để bị ăn.{weaklings like us are simply picked off and eaten.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:39.52,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,1,Kẻ yếu chỉ có thể chọn con đường của kẻ yếu thôi.{Weaklings have no choice}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.78,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Riko, vào trong nhanh lên!{Riko, hurry and get further inside!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.08,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Cái gì thế?{What was that...?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.50,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:06:00.59,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Thành công rồi! Cái hang này có đường đi xuống!{We did it! This den extends way, way down!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.71,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nhanh lên! Nhanh lên!{Hey! Quick! Hurry up!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.17,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,À, tới ngay đây.{Ah, I'm coming now.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.55,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Âm thanh đó...{That sound...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.72,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,1,Nghe hơi quen nhỉ? {Nó kéo theo gì đó nhỉ?{Something about it bothers me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.85,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Xuống sâu kha khá rồi đấy nhỉ.{We've descended quite a ways.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.48,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Cũng phải.{Yeah...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:21.69,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,1,Nhưng vì để tiến tới, mà mình phá cái tổ nó dữ quá.{Still, I know it was for the sake of pushing forward, but we totally trashed this den.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.78,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Phải cảm ơn bọn chúng rồi.{We should be grateful to these little guys.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:30.45,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Ừ, nhờ chúng mà ta chẳng gặp rắc rối nào về thức ăn hay chỗ ngủ.{Yeah, thanks to them we haven't had any trouble}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:35.66,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Chúng chủ yếu ăn trái Baracocha, nên thịt khá mềm và ngon.{And they primarily live on Baracocha fruit,}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.38,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nơi này... là một tàn tích sao?{Are these some kind of ruins?}
