Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.14,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Đây là một phần của cái thuyền!{This is part of a ship!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.73,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Từ rất rất lâu rồi.{One from a long, long time ago!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.69,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Thuyền?!{"A ship"?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.31,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Không biết còn Di tích nào bên trong không...{I wonder if there are still any Relics inside...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.82,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nhưng sao ở đây lại có thuyền?{But, why is there a ship here in the first place...?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.07,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Có Di tích nào không đây?{Any Relics out there?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:15.03,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Này, Di tích ơi...?{Hello there! Relics...?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:25.54,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Cái gì thế này?{What's this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.72,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Đây là...{This is...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:36.47,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,tổ của Madoka Jack...{a madokajack's...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.70,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nhanh quá!{It's so quick!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.74,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Phóng tay ra cũng sẽ bị nó gặm lấy mất!{Even if I hurl my fists at it, they'll just get chomped on!}
