Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.01,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Hay quá!{Way to go!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.68,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Không biết Madoka Jack có vị thế nào...{I wonder how madokajacks taste...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.60,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Riko! Nghe kĩ đây...{Riko! Listen to me!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.89,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Tớ sắp sửa ngất đi rồi!{I'm going to fall asleep before long now that I did that!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.27,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,2 tiếng...{Two hours...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.11,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Trong thời gian đó, cậu...{During that time, you'll be-}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:16.78,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Vừa nãy cũng nghe thấy, là gì mới được?{I heard it earlier, too, but what the heck is that?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.66,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Tiếng gào này...{That cry...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.29,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Là Beni Kuchinawa...{Could it be a crimson splitjaw...?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:23.95,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Chạy thôi!{Run!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.09,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Trên đầu có vết thương?{There's a wound on its head?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.42,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nó là con bị Reg dùng Đại bác lửa {đại hỏa pháo}bắn!{That must be the one Reg blasted with his Incinerator!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.17,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Hình như chúng có tổ ở tầng 3...{I know I heard they have lairs on the third layer...}
