Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.94,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Mình sắp... thiếp đi...{I'm gonna... faint...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.61,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Tránh... ra... đi mà!{Outta my way!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.16,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Á! Tới rồi!{Yikes! There it is!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:06.50,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Tránh ra đi mà!{I'm begging you, let me through!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.23,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Không sao chứ Reg?!{You alright, Reg?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:34.98,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Riko, ở đây đến lúc tớ tỉnh lại...{Riko, until I wake up, stay right here...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.53,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Không sao đâu!{It'll be fine!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.49,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Tớ sẽ bảo vệ Reg mà!{Reg, I'll protect you, okay?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.54,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Đói quá...{I sure am hungry...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.71,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Tìm cái gì ăn thôi...{I need to look for some food.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.96,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Cũng không thể để Reg nằm đây được...{And I can't leave Reg lying here, anyway...}
