Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:37.67,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Chịu...{I...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.47,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,hết nổi...{can't...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.55,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,rồi!{keep going!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.10,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Không đi nổi nữa. {Hết đi nổi.{I can't press on.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.60,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Đợi ở đây đến khi Reg tỉnh lại vậy...{I'll wait here until Reg wakes up...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:56.40,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Ơ?{Huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.61,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Là mùi Baracocha!{That's the smell of Baracochas!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.74,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nhất định có quả ở quanh đây!{They must be bearing fruit somewhere below me!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.45,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Lucky!{How lucky!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:18.96,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Gần lắm rồi!{I'm close now!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:20.88,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Baracocha đâu nhể?{Where are the Baracochas?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:22.38,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Đâu nào?{Where?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.39,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Ở đâu, ở đâu?{Where, oh where?}
