Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.96,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Mùi Baracocha thật nồng nặc...{This intense scent of Baracochas...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.83,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Chỗ này rốt cuộc là sao...{What the heck is this place...?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:57.63,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Ơ?{Huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:00.55,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Đây là...{Is that...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.22,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,đuôi Neritantan? {a Neritantan tail?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.05,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Không lẽ là...{Could it be...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:10.47,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,bên trong bụng con Amakagame sao?!{that I'm inside the stomach on an Amakagame?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.10,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Chết toi!{Damn it!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:15.77,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Mùi này nhất định là để dụ lũ Neritantan đến đây!{This scent must be a trap meant to lure Neritantans here!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.86,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Mau rời khỏi đây thôi, không thì tiêu mất.{I need to get out of here quick}
