Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:33.60,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Tao có phải Baracocha đâu!{I'm not Baracocha fruit, okay?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.06,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Ui!{Ouch!}
