Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.48,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Thành công rồi...{I did it...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.95,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Không phải chứ...{You've gotta be kidding me...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.78,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Sao lại là con dốc đi lên?{Why's there an upward slope?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.66,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Không được rồi!{There's no way!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:37.33,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nếu leo lên sẽ dính lời nguyền mất...{If I ascend that much, the Curse will-}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:46.17,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nhưng... không còn đường quay lại nữa...{But, I can't turn back now...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.13,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Reg... đi thôi.{Reg... here we go.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:12.53,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Lời nguyền ở Tầng 3:{The strain of the depths' third layer:}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.87,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,nhức đầu, chóng mặt...{headaches, dizziness...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.54,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,buồn nôn...{...severe nausea...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.42,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Ngoài ra còn...{in addition to...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.42,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,gặp các vấn đề về giác quan.{problems with your sense of balance.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:29.42,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Họ đây rồi! Sư phụ! {There they are! Master!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.68,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Giờ cậu có thể an tâm rồi, Riko!{You can relax now, Riko!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.59,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Marulk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.01,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Đúng thế.{That's right.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:42.43,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nào, cùng quay lại với chúng ta đi thôi?{Well now, won't you head back with us?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.65,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Thị giác, thính giác gặp ảo giác...{Visual and auditory hallucinations...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.40,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Đủ rồi mà, Riko.{That's enough already, Riko.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.94,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nghỉ chút đi, đừng cố quá!{Take a break. Don't overdo it now!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.70,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:55.74,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Mọi người...{Everybody...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:59.33,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Làm tốt lắm, Riko! Còn lại cứ để bác!{You did great, Riko! Just leave the rest to me!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.20,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Bác Habo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:03.75,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.71,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Mẹ...{Mom...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:13.22,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Riko, cùng quay lại thôi... về Orth.{Riko, let's go back together... back to Orth.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.80,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Mẹ ơi!{Mom!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.77,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Mẹ ơi, đây là đâu vậy?{Mom, where are we?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:29.90,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Là gondola quay lên Orth.{We're inside a gondola that's heading to Orth.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:31.61,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Ơ?!{Huh?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.49,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nhưng còn lời nguyền Abyss thì sao?{But what about the Curse of the Abyss?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.74,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Không sao hết...{It's alright...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:38.53,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Cơ thể con không còn chịu ảnh hưởng của lời nguyền nữa.{Your body is no longer affected by the Curse.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.53,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nào, sắp tới rồi.{Well, we're about to arrive.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.50,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Là thành phố Orth!{It's the city of Orth!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.39,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Chào mừng trở về!{Welcome home!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:08.40,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.65,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Chào mừng trở lại!{Welcome back home!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:11.06,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.32,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.61,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Mọi người!{Everyone...!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.07,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Tôi về rồi đây!{I'm home!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:26.91,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Reg?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:29.17,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Reg đâu rồi?{Where's Reg?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:35.17,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Mẹ! Reg đâu, Reg đâu rồi!{Mom! What about Reg?! Reg's not here!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.17,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Reg đang...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.05,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,ở dưới đáy Abyss rồi...{at the bottom of the netherworld.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.55,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nhưng tại sao?{But why...?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.06,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Con không muốn!{I won't have it!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:44.97,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nếu Reg không đi cùng...{If Reg's not here with me...}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:47.73,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,thì về Orth còn ý nghĩa gì nữa chứ!{there's no point in me even returning to Orth!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.44,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Bọn con luôn bên nhau...{The two of us were always together...}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.57,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Reg... Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.15,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nếu không phải là cùng với Reg...{If I'm not together with Reg...}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.99,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,thì không chịu đâu!{I can't bear it!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:19.67,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Giờ mới thấy một mình leo xuống Abyss khó khăn nhường nào.{Now I see how hard it is}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:26.77,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Tớ vẫn luôn được cậu bảo vệ mà...{I was being protected by you all along...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.23,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.44,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Đủ rồi!{Enough!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.24,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Mi phiền phức quá!{You sure are pesky!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:40.15,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,A, đúng rồi!{Ah, that's right!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:46.74,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:54.33,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Cho mi biết bác Ozen đã dạy ta cách dùng rồi nhé!{Ozen taught me how to use this thing, you know!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:02.18,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:07.22,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Reg! Dùng nó đi! {Use this!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.58,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.33,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi, tớ dậy trễ.{Sorry I took so long.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.42,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Không sao...{Don't be...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:41.42,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nhờ thế mà tớ ngộ ra nhiều điều.{It allowed me to think about lots of stuff.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.72,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,À mà tớ hiểu rồi.{Speaking of that, I understand now.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:44.72,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Hiểu gì cơ?{You understand?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.72,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Rằng nếu chỉ có một mình, nhất định tớ không làm được.{That if I was on my own,}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.06,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nhờ có Reg, tớ mới tiến xa được tới mức này.{Reg, it's thanks to you that I was able to make it this far.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.98,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn nhé, Reg!{Thank you, Reg!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:55.77,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Ơ, ừm...{Y-yeah...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.98,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Chính tớ cũng vậy thôi.{I feel the same way.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:01.65,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Vì là Riko...{It's because I had Riko with me...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:04.28,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Vì là hai chúng ta... mới được thế này.{It's because it's the two of us... that we made it here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.42,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Quanh đây giờ lại xuất hiện nhiều mũi nhọn nhở.{The landscape around here has become a lot spikier.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:17.13,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Độ sâu là...{Our depth is...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.17,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,để xem...{Let's see...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:22.13,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,6750m à?{6,750 meters, I think.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.88,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Nghe đâu mấy mũi nhọn này thực ra là trứng...{I hear these spikes are actually eggs...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.89,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Có cách nào chế biến không nhỉ...{I wonder if there's a way to make them into a tasty meal...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:33.27,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Riko, tớ thấy bên dưới rồi!{Riko, I can see something down there!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:53.41,MIB - Dialouge,,0,0,0,,Là Chén của Người khổng lồ!{It's the Goblet of Giants!}
